-- Alstom Confirms Operating Margin Forecast; Sales Close to Analyst Estimate
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-20T06:06:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/alstom-confirms-operating-margin-forecast-sales-close-to-analyst-estimate.html

          
          
              Alstom SA said in an emailed
statement that first-quarter sales were 4.74 billion euros, in
line with analyst estimates for 4.75 billion euros.  
 The company confirmed its forecast for an operating margin
of between 7 percent and 8 percent in 2010-11 and 2011-12, based
on a gradual recovery of demand.  
          
          


  


        